<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" id="login2">
    <head>
        <title>Login</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8"></meta>
        <script src="/gtm-id.js"></script>
        %INCLUDES%
    </head>
    <body class="chaise-body">
        <div class="configure-container" ng-app="chaise.configure-login2">
            <loading-spinner></loading-spinner>
        </div>
        <div class="app-container container-fluid row" ng-controller="Login2Controller as ctrl">
            <div ng-if="showInstructions" class="login2-container main-container">
                <h2>Sign up for personalized dashboard features</h2>
                <p>To access the personalized dashboard features, membership in the "{{ctrl.groupName}}" group is required. Click the <b>Sign Up</b> button to join the group. Using the <b>Sign Up</b> button will open a Globus group enrollment page in a separate tab or window. After completing enrollment on that page, come back and click the <b>Proceed</b> button to begin using the new features of this site.</p>
                <div class="btn-container">
                    <a class="chaise-btn chaise-btn-primary" ng-href="{{::ctrl.joinLink}}" target="_blank" uib-tooltip-html="'{{'Click to sign up for <code>' + ctrl.groupName + '</code>.'}}'" tooltip-placement="bottom-left">Sign Up</a>
                    <button class="chaise-btn chaise-btn-secondary" ng-click="::ctrl.reLogin()" uib-tooltip="Click to proceed to the application after joining the group." tooltip-placement="bottom-left">Proceed</button>
                </div>
                <loading-spinner ng-show="showSpinner"></loading-spinner>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
